titles.title: To suspend temporarily the duty on 2,2'-methylenebisY6-(1,1-dimethylethyl)-4-phenol.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.
Referred to the Subcommittee on Trade.

bill.summary:
12/17/2007--Introduced.
Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend temporarily the duty on 2,2'-methylenebisY6-(1,1-dimethylethyl)-4-phenol.
